John Brynarsky's son Chris was shot and killed in his custom car detail shop in October 2006 . 
  When he was shot, he fell over a bumper he was working on and damaged it . 
  His friend Mark Cosentino repaired the bumper and wrote an inscription on the inside dedicated to his slain son . 
  On Good Friday, John was working in his body shop in Charlotte and found the inscription . 
 